snippet.title: PICROSS S3 Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
This is the 3rd Picross S Series on the Nintendo Switch!
The eagerly anticipated Color Picross from the Picross S Series is finally here!
Complete color illustrations using colorful hint numbers!

The offial site is here
http://www.jupiter.co.jp/e/switch/picrosss3/index.html
